result.name: Shatin Galleria

reviews.text:
Shatin Galleria is a small two-floor complex on Shan Mei Street in the industrial area of Fo Tan. There are a handful of small restaurants, fast-food places and coffee shops that can get rather filled up at meal times by those who work in this area. I stop by from time to time to eat at a place here called Asra, a surprisingly good place for Indian food. 

You can also find bank branches, pharmacy, few retail and other shops serving those work in the area and live nearby. That is pretty much it when it comes to the Shatin Galleria in Fo Tan.
The place hasn't change for years time for major renovation

October 28, 2018 update: There was an escalator accident happened in the afternoon causing two people injured. The escalators brand is Dong Yang (東洋). Beware of your safety when you use the facility.
----
Toilets on office floors and on shopping floors are always dirty. Elevators and escalators are always out of service. At night time, most restaurants close at 6pm except Mc Donald's. The building is far away from KCR station. Basically it is a dead old place where no one want to stay for long time.
Nice place to spend a day shopping, relax and have meals
Elevators and escalators are always broken. Ok food selection. ATMS available.

reviews.text: 可能假期，得一間平民化嘅快餐小食開業，除咗麥當奴，KFC ，一間酒樓，就冇其它選擇
自動電梯繼續維修中，有上冇落，有幾間食肆，惠康，759，銀行等，還有2元港鐵拍卡優惠👈
樓上的 歌美咖啡店 食物飲品好味，新鮮!! 服務員態度親切，
呢個商場，電梯可以壞足成年咁耐？好啦，年頭整好，但又壞左另一部？係米又等成年先整好呢

result.name: 肯德基

reviews.text: 出餐極慢，想外賣拎走，等一個包等左足足超過二十分鐘都仲話整緊，要我等多兩分鐘(我係嚟食快餐㗎！)啲員工分工都有問題，個個堆哂喺後面唔知做咩，櫃台又冇人接單收錢，話咩前面啲單未整完，所以唔接住。嗰一粒星只係俾嗰度有禮貌嘅清潔人員。。。
雞件偏細件，但出餐速度算快員工工作效率高。
我只是食磨菇飯及飲杯蜜綠茶就夠食飽，其他日後再嘗試，肯德基的食品品質都唔錯，份量多，坐位環境很舒服、寬闊、分店多，值得常去的店舖。
工業區，人流不多，員工也不多所以整潔一般，食物品質大至其他一樣，但有一個好處坐行久也沒有理會

Would rather this be a Jolly bee. Easily one of the worst fast food outlets in HK considering how quiet it is most of the time. Slow, slow slow kitchen team and they ALWAYS forget something.. Napkins, sauce, fork/spoon. Absolutely no quality control and I really hope KFC shuts down worldwide. You guys are an insult to food!
